items.headline: Welcome to WikiSein, the Seinfeld Wiki!
items.desc: WikiSein is the Wiki about Nothing. It is a work in progress for the television series Seinfeld, and all the media/merchandise that spawned from it. It chronicles the adventures of Jerry, George, Kramer, and Elaine across New York. Pages are being added fast, and all contributions are wanted and encouraged.
